      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "title": "Make port permission explicit and bounded",
        "body": "Define an explicit port capability ladder so navigation, view consumption, bridging, and runtime invocation stay intentionally separate. Adopt `navigate`, `consume-view`, `bridge`, and `runtime` as the working levels, with plain navigate as the default.",
