    {
      "id": "port-permission-model-note-scripted-views",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Host-Owned Port Permission",
      "position": {
        "x": 1160,
        "y": 700
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Host-Owned Port Permission\n\nEvery new port is created on the host graph with a default permission of `navigate`.\n\nEscalation law:\n\n- the host graph owns the port instance\n- the host graph may edit the port permission explicitly\n- the field name is `authority`\n- `authority` is edited in node properties\n- `authority` is not edited in the view panel\n- `consume-view` is explicit\n- `bridge` is explicit\n- `runtime` is explicit and rare\n- no higher capability is inferred automatically from the target graph",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "views": [
            {
              "key": "markdown",
              "intent": "editor",
              "payload": "editor.web",
              "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
              "source": "local",
              "version": ">=0.1.0"
            },
            {
